and absolutely like a mad person. But the police said,

00:17:14.070 --> 00:17:15.200
"Nothing doing, now you’d better put her

00:17:16.020 --> 00:17:17.070
in the old mad ones’ place."

00:17:17.180 --> 00:17:20.180
So she put her in one of these places

00:17:21.030 --> 00:17:22.210
