01:13:18.230 --> 01:13:20.220
It is very important, it gets swollen up

01:13:21.080 --> 01:13:23.110
and a big barrier is built

01:13:23.220 --> 01:13:26.200
and you become a person completely cut off

01:13:27.040 --> 01:13:28.150
from the all-pervading Power.

01:13:28.230 --> 01:13:31.140
Means all the protections, all the guidance,

01:13:31.230 --> 01:13:34.170
all the nurturing things, everything

01:13:35.000 --> 01:13:38.090
starts disappearing from your life.

01:13:39.210 --> 01:13:44.070
Now we go ahead with that centre to the centre here,

01:13:44.140 --> 01:13:46.190
which is very important and which I must tell you, though,

01:13:47.030 --> 01:13:50.020
it's time to finish this lecture,

01:13:50.170 --> 01:13:55.060
is the centre of Agnya

01:13:55.170 --> 01:13:58.140
which is placed in the

01:13:59.190 --> 01:14:03.030
centre of pituitary and pineal body

01:14:03.120 --> 01:14:06.080
which controls our ego and superego,

01:14:06.160 --> 01:14:09.230
between the optic chiasma, a very subtle centre exists.

01:14:10.060 --> 01:14:11.110
Some people call it a third eye

01:14:11.200 --> 01:14:15.050
but the third eye they see is not the one I am talking about.

01:14:15.140 --> 01:14:21.060
The third eye means the eye we see it inside not outside.

01:14:22.230 --> 01:14:26.060
This centre is very important

01:14:26.140 --> 01:14:30.140
and is adorned by the deity

01:14:36.000 --> 01:14:39.160
of Mahavishnu according to Indian name

01:14:39.240 --> 01:14:44.100
and English name is Lord Jesus Christ.

01:14:44.240 --> 01:14:46.220
This is a very important centre.

01:14:47.070 --> 01:14:49.100
"Now seek your Lord."

01:14:49.180 --> 01:14:51.240
Where do you seek Him? Where does He exist?

01:14:52.120 --> 01:14:55.210
He's to be awakened and He resides here

01:14:56.040 --> 01:14:58.120
because most of you are coming from that background

01:14:58.190 --> 01:14:59.190
I want to talk about it,

01:15:00.020 --> 01:15:02.100
though Mahavira and Mahabuddha

01:15:02.230 --> 01:15:05.010
both of them also reside within us:

01:15:05.090 --> 01:15:09.040
Mahavira resides here and Buddha resides here.

01:15:09.150 --> 01:15:14.230
But Christ resides here in the centre, inside the brain.

01:15:15.210 --> 01:15:19.210
Now this is a very important thing

01:15:20.050 --> 01:15:22.090
which all the Christian institutions

01:15:22.150 --> 01:15:25.020
have missed about Christ.

01:15:25.150 --> 01:15:28.150
That Christ is to be born within us.

01:15:28.240 --> 01:15:31.180
That He's to be awakened within us.

01:15:32.020 --> 01:15:35.070
That is only done through Kundalini awakening

01:15:35.180 --> 01:15:39.040
and once He's awakened, at that point,

01:15:39.130 --> 01:15:42.130
ego and superego both are sucked by Him,

01:15:42.230 --> 01:15:44.100
as a result of His awakening

01:15:44.190 --> 01:15:46.190
and this is a very big thing.

01:15:47.050 --> 01:15:49.200
That's why He said, "I am the door."

01:15:50.130 --> 01:15:52.090
But very nice, they crucified Him.

01:15:52.180 --> 01:15:54.230
But that crucifixion was also a drama,

01:15:55.070 --> 01:15:59.230
because ego and superego has pressed this point so hard,

01:16:00.050 --> 01:16:03.010
that to pass through that you needed somebody

01:16:03.090 --> 01:16:06.230
to be just divine, and He was Omkara Himself,

01:16:07.050 --> 01:16:08.100
the divine personality

01:16:08.190 --> 01:16:12.040
Who never died and passed through that.

01:16:13.020 --> 01:16:16.040
Krishna has said, Who is at this point,

01:16:16.150 --> 01:16:17.120
has said that “Nayanam chidanti shastrani,

01:16:17.210 --> 01:16:20.150
nayanam dahati pavaka.” He said,

01:16:21.120 --> 01:16:27.130
"This divine power, this Omkara,

01:16:28.030 --> 01:16:30.090
never can be killed by anyone,

01:16:30.190 --> 01:16:33.080
it cannot be destroyed by anyone,"

01:16:34.050 --> 01:16:40.160
and this itself took the birth of Jesus Christ.

01:16:41.030 --> 01:16:43.200
To create that passage for us.

01:16:45.110 --> 01:16:50.090
And that is the thing He proved, that it cannot be killed.

01:16:50.190 --> 01:16:53.080
But They are all One and related to each other.

01:16:53.170 --> 01:16:55.220
This you'll discover in Sahaja Yoga itself

01:16:56.080 --> 01:16:58.140
because when the rapport is established,

01:16:59.000 --> 01:17:00.110
you have to ask questions.

01:17:00.190 --> 01:17:04.190
What is the relationship between Jesus and Krishna?

01:17:05.080 --> 01:17:07.140
And you can discover it on vibrations:

01:17:08.060 --> 01:17:11.090
They are all related to each other, very closely.

01:17:11.180 --> 01:17:14.170
Christ has said, "Those who are not against Me are with Me."

01:17:15.010 --> 01:17:17.110
Nobody has tried to find out who are those.

01:17:18.000 --> 01:17:19.060
It is said in the Bible that

01:17:19.140 --> 01:17:21.080
"I'll appear before you like tongues of flames."

01:17:21.150 --> 01:17:24.110
Nobody tried to find out what is that, or Tree of Life -

01:17:24.180 --> 01:17:27.030
is this the Tree of Life.

01:17:27.240 --> 01:17:29.220
So He is to be awakened within you,

01:17:30.050 --> 01:17:32.210
that's the main point that He said that

01:17:33.020 --> 01:17:36.070
"Somebody will come and awaken it,

01:17:36.160 --> 01:17:39.080
so that you will know My Father forever."

01:17:39.190 --> 01:17:41.130
Now which one of the institutions

01:17:41.220 --> 01:17:45.020
which are running in the name of our Lord Jesus Christ

01:17:45.100 --> 01:17:46.080
are doing that job?

01:17:46.180 --> 01:17:48.210
What they are doing is having a fete, or a carnival,

01:17:49.050 --> 01:17:51.220
collecting money, building churches, this, that.

01:17:52.050 --> 01:17:54.140
You have to build every human being as a church

01:17:54.220 --> 01:17:57.210
by awakening Christ in them.

01:17:58.050 --> 01:18:01.050
That was what was meant by baptism.

01:18:01.130 --> 01:18:03.220
But whom did baptism in the real sense

01:18:04.050 --> 01:18:06.210
is the Kundalini awakening when it comes

01:18:08.220 --> 01:18:10.170
on the fontanel bone area which is called

01:18:11.000 --> 01:18:13.190
as the brahmarandhra, and breaks through that.

01:18:14.080 --> 01:18:18.020
Who has done that? None.

01:18:18.140 --> 01:18:21.050
I went to a church called Unity Church,

01:18:21.140 --> 01:18:23.140
they have united all the churches I believe

01:18:23.220 --> 01:18:26.030
and also united all the ghosts of the world.

01:18:26.120 --> 01:18:29.090
All kinds of fake gurus are there, all kinds,

01:18:29.160 --> 01:18:32.140
they have no discrimination of any kind.

01:18:34.220 --> 01:18:37.230
I am so amazed, you know. Christ,

01:18:38.230 --> 01:18:41.000
He was not so diplomatic I should say

01:18:41.090 --> 01:18:44.090
because the way He lashed at these people and then He said,

01:18:44.200 --> 01:18:46.200
"If they are hot, we can manage them" -

01:18:47.030 --> 01:18:48.160
means “if they are hot” means they're caught up,

01:18:48.230 --> 01:18:51.190
we'll manage them: if they are cold, we like them;

01:18:52.080 --> 01:18:56.030
but if they are half-way, "I spit them out of My mouth."

01:18:56.160 --> 01:18:57.170
These are His words.

01:18:58.000 --> 01:19:02.110
Because these half-baked people compromising with the devil,

01:19:02.190 --> 01:19:04.170
and talking of God.

01:19:05.050 --> 01:19:07.130
How are they going to deliver the goods?

01:19:09.080 --> 01:19:11.160
Why not awaken your Christ within yourself

01:19:11.220 --> 01:19:13.090
and see for yourself?

01:19:13.190 --> 01:19:15.160
You'll be amazed when you raise the Kundalini

01:19:15.230 --> 01:19:17.120
and Kundalini comes up to this point

01:19:17.220 --> 01:19:19.140
and it cannot go further,

01:19:19.220 --> 01:19:21.140
among all the Christians this is a problem.

01:19:21.220 --> 01:19:24.170
You have to ask them to say Lord's Prayer, and it works,

01:19:25.020 --> 01:19:26.110
that's a mantra.

01:19:29.090 --> 01:19:32.020
At the time when your, this centre is catching,

01:19:32.110 --> 01:19:36.060
because Krishna is a Collective Being,

01:19:36.160 --> 01:19:38.200
"Allah hu Akbar" means the same.

01:19:39.030 --> 01:19:41.060
You have to put your fingers into your ears and say,

01:19:41.140 --> 01:19:44.070
"Allah hu Akbar" realized souls,

01:19:44.180 --> 01:19:46.180
and you'll get the kundalini rising.

01:19:47.010 --> 01:19:48.180
You can see the pulsation of the Kundalini

01:19:49.000 --> 01:19:49.230
at the triangular bone,

01:19:50.040 --> 01:19:51.110
you can see the rising of the Kundalini,

01:19:51.170 --> 01:19:55.200
you can feel the breaking of Kundalini at the Sahasrara

01:19:56.010 --> 01:19:58.180
at the point where it comes and breaks it.

01:19:59.180 --> 01:20:02.060
So you enter through the gate of Christ

01:20:02.140 --> 01:20:05.010
who sucks these two institutions

01:20:05.120 --> 01:20:07.090
and makes the way here,

01:20:08.170 --> 01:20:10.130
and once the Kundalini rises above the Agnya,

01:20:10.190 --> 01:20:11.220
you become thoughtless.

01:20:12.090 --> 01:20:17.040
The limbic area is the Kingdom of God

01:20:17.120 --> 01:20:21.200
from where you are guided and the Kundalini passes through.

01:20:22.120 --> 01:20:24.030
That's the last job that is to be done,

01:20:24.110 --> 01:20:26.220
and now it is done.

01:20:27.170 --> 01:20:29.190
That is done now en masse.

01:20:30.010 --> 01:20:32.140
It has to be done, it was to be done,

01:20:32.220 --> 01:20:35.200
it was promised, the time has come.

01:20:36.240 --> 01:20:39.210
But where are the people, sometimes I wonder?

01:20:40.190 --> 01:20:42.160
I am in England now with you;

01:20:43.020 --> 01:20:47.160
you'll be amazed that in India, these people have seen,

01:20:48.020 --> 01:20:51.210
thousands and thousands are there to receive Realization

01:20:52.050 --> 01:20:53.060
in the villages.

