Here I find people don't want reality,

01:20:57.060 --> 01:20:58.220
you should have a circus.

01:20:59.070 --> 01:21:02.040
At least English people come but Indians very few

01:21:02.120 --> 01:21:03.210
and they never stick on.

01:21:04.020 --> 01:21:06.240
It’s so amazing that I can't understand.

01:21:07.100 --> 01:21:10.050
It's amazing how things work out.

01:21:12.040 --> 01:21:14.130
When are we going to take to it?

01:21:14.210 --> 01:21:18.010
I mean it's free, you don't have to pay anything,

01:21:18.090 --> 01:21:20.240
it's your own, it is spontaneous, it is there.

01:21:21.120 --> 01:21:25.050
But still, they get Realization, they get lost.

01:21:25.150 --> 01:21:27.040
It's something so surprising,

01:21:27.130 --> 01:21:30.120
I've been working here, you won't believe, ten years now,

01:21:30.190 --> 01:21:32.040
eight years, eight years.

01:21:33.000 --> 01:21:37.030
For four years, in the first four years I had six people,

01:21:37.140 --> 01:21:40.020
they would come up, go down, come up, go down.

01:21:40.110 --> 01:21:42.110
I said, "What sort of people?"

01:21:43.000 --> 01:21:45.120
Four years, can you imagine?

01:21:45.220 --> 01:21:49.170
In India, I go for three months and I get thousands.

01:21:51.030 --> 01:21:53.170
Is it that there are very few who are going to be saved,

01:21:54.000 --> 01:21:55.030
as told by John?

01:21:55.110 --> 01:21:58.030
He said only a few thousand are going to be saved,

01:21:58.110 --> 01:22:01.110
is that what we are going to do in the West?

01:22:01.240 --> 01:22:03.190
But England is the minimum,

01:22:04.030 --> 01:22:06.240
you'll be amazed even Italy is better,

01:22:07.090 --> 01:22:11.050
Switzerland, Geneva, so much better, what's happening?

01:22:11.130 --> 01:22:16.090
Here they run after a man who is asking for a Rolls Royce,

01:22:17.080 --> 01:22:19.050
a fellow who asks for a 59-th Rolls Royce,

01:22:19.130 --> 01:22:21.020
they starve themselves

01:22:21.090 --> 01:22:23.170
and made a Rolls Royce for him and when he came,

01:22:24.000 --> 01:22:25.140
they gave him the Rolls Royce, imagine?

01:22:26.000 --> 01:22:27.220
They said he's a perfect master.

01:22:28.050 --> 01:22:30.080
There is no pure intelligence left in the mind

01:22:30.140 --> 01:22:32.240
to understand that how can you get Spirit

01:22:33.050 --> 01:22:35.170
for this nonsensical Rolls Royce?

01:22:36.130 --> 01:22:39.060
At least Derbyshire are not, people from Derbyshire

01:22:39.130 --> 01:22:41.190
should not be impressed by that very much,

01:22:42.050 --> 01:22:44.140
because they make it here.

01:22:45.190 --> 01:22:48.060
You cannot make God, can you?

01:22:48.200 --> 01:22:51.000
You can make Rolls Royces, all right,

01:22:51.100 --> 01:22:53.240
can you exchange Rolls Royce for God?

01:22:54.160 --> 01:22:56.130
They are running after such horrible things,

01:22:56.200 --> 01:22:58.140
like horrible another thing that somebody

01:22:58.200 --> 01:23:00.100
is trying to teach you how to fly.

01:23:00.190 --> 01:23:02.130
The wife of the director is sitting here

01:23:02.210 --> 01:23:04.200
who started is suffering with epilepsy -

01:23:05.020 --> 01:23:07.030
her husband got epilepsy, her daughter got epilepsy,

01:23:07.130 --> 01:23:08.170
they all were epileptic,

01:23:09.000 --> 01:23:10.240
and they were paying thousands of pounds,

01:23:11.050 --> 01:23:13.080
three thousand pounds to fly,

01:23:13.160 --> 01:23:18.130
and they starting hopping themselves like a frog. Imagine!

01:23:19.170 --> 01:23:21.130
With pure intelligence you must ask

01:23:21.220 --> 01:23:25.200
that guru to drop himself from the leaning Tower of Pisa,

01:23:26.030 --> 01:23:27.190
I think it was made only for that,

01:23:28.050 --> 01:23:32.240
and see if he can fly even one inch higher.

01:23:33.210 --> 01:23:35.170
Why not use your intelligence?

01:23:35.230 --> 01:23:37.180
You are supposed to be most balanced

01:23:38.010 --> 01:23:40.010
and intelligent people.

01:23:41.070 --> 01:23:44.000
Yesterday I told you that you are placed,

01:23:44.110 --> 01:23:48.160
the most important place in the Universe is the Heart,

01:23:49.000 --> 01:23:51.070
England is the Heart of the Universe

01:23:51.170 --> 01:23:54.220
and the Heart is lethargic.

01:23:56.030 --> 01:23:57.050
What can I do?

01:23:57.130 --> 01:23:59.130
You have to tell Me, what am I to do,

01:23:59.210 --> 01:24:02.180
to pump this Heart into reality.

01:24:03.020 --> 01:24:05.020
There are seekers, I would not say there are seekers,

01:24:05.080 --> 01:24:08.240
When it came to hippieism, thousands became hippies.

01:24:09.140 --> 01:24:11.210
But all absurd things they accept very easily

01:24:12.030 --> 01:24:15.110
and why not the thing that you are seeking?

01:24:16.020 --> 01:24:18.160
It's beyond My mind. I cannot understand.

01:24:18.240 --> 01:24:21.020
Now I didn't come to this place as an immigrant, as I told

01:24:21.080 --> 01:24:25.050
you. I was, just came, I came here because something happened

01:24:25.130 --> 01:24:27.140
and My husband got elected to this country,

01:24:27.240 --> 01:24:29.190
which was important, which was,

01:24:30.030 --> 01:24:32.240
I think, was pre-ordained. It was to be.

01:24:33.130 --> 01:24:37.220
But I have to implore you now to take to this and understand

01:24:38.160 --> 01:24:40.160
that this is what William Blake has told you

01:24:40.220 --> 01:24:46.190
that "The prophets are going to be in this country,

01:24:47.080 --> 01:24:49.200
that the God of men are going to become prophets

01:24:50.020 --> 01:24:51.170
and they are going to have the power

01:24:51.240 --> 01:24:54.000
to make others prophets." That is Sahaja Yoga.

01:24:54.110 --> 01:24:56.240
There's nothing else but this.

01:24:58.150 --> 01:25:00.000
He has promised so many things.

01:25:00.080 --> 01:25:03.050
He has even described the house where I live,

01:25:03.140 --> 01:25:06.000
he has described the house that we are occupying now,

01:25:06.080 --> 01:25:07.170
exact position.

01:25:07.230 --> 01:25:11.230
He has described the ashram where we'll lay our foundations,

01:25:12.230 --> 01:25:18.120
into such details that I'm amazed such a great sage

01:25:18.200 --> 01:25:20.140
and a seer was born in this great country

01:25:20.220 --> 01:25:24.060
and nobody wants to see it through. Now what am I to do?

01:25:26.020 --> 01:25:31.110
I hope very soon people would realize

01:25:32.090 --> 01:25:35.200
that they have to take a very big role,

01:25:36.090 --> 01:25:39.110
a very important and vital role

01:25:39.220 --> 01:25:42.060
in the transformation of the whole humanity

01:25:42.160 --> 01:25:46.060
and saving of this disastrous time.

01:25:46.220 --> 01:25:48.230
They are the ones who have to lead people

01:25:49.060 --> 01:25:51.090
into the Kingdom of God.

01:25:51.220 --> 01:25:54.020
I can hope and bless that.

01:25:54.110 --> 01:25:57.170
May God bless you!

01:26:03.220 --> 01:26:07.180
Luckily we have a very good standard

01:26:08.110 --> 01:26:10.150
of the Sahaja Yogis in Derbyshire,

01:26:11.010 --> 01:26:12.180
really it's surprising

01:26:13.040 --> 01:26:16.240
and Blake has mentioned Derbyshire very much,

01:26:17.120 --> 01:26:19.010
they wanted Me to come to Derbyshire.

01:26:19.080 --> 01:26:21.050
I said, "Birmingham has been sufficient for Me

01:26:21.110 --> 01:26:22.120
and I am not going to Derbyshire."

01:26:22.190 --> 01:26:24.010
And they said, "Mother, please." And then he said,

01:26:24.090 --> 01:26:26.080
"Blake has mentioned You come to Derbyshire."

01:26:26.160 --> 01:26:27.200
And that's how I am here

01:26:28.040 --> 01:26:32.090
and I hope that this centre will definitely create

01:26:32.180 --> 01:26:34.120
very good Sahaja Yogis.

01:26:34.230 --> 01:26:38.230
Great prophets can be created out of this,

01:26:39.060 --> 01:26:42.100
after all Blake has mentioned Derbyshire very strongly,

01:26:42.200 --> 01:26:43.170
he recommended it.

01:26:43.230 --> 01:26:46.060
But what I find today when I went for a drive,

01:26:46.150 --> 01:26:48.100
there's a lot of black magic on.

01:26:48.200 --> 01:26:52.210
People are indulging into horrible, horrible things.

01:26:53.090 --> 01:26:56.150
I was worried, quite worried.

01:26:57.040 --> 01:26:59.030
It's a very dangerous thing.

01:26:59.210 --> 01:27:01.230
It's dangerous for you, for your children,

01:27:02.040 --> 01:27:04.120
for your families, for everyone,

01:27:04.210 --> 01:27:06.170
and I found those pockets,

01:27:07.030 --> 01:27:09.210
I was amazed how they are prospering here.

01:27:10.070 --> 01:27:15.140
May God give you strength and proper wisdom

01:27:15.230 --> 01:27:20.000
to understand how you are placed in relation

01:27:20.170 --> 01:27:23.100
to the great work of God.

