Now don't ask personal questions for heaven's sake,

01:27:43.070 --> 01:27:44.210
don't ask any personal question.

01:27:45.030 --> 01:27:47.170
That we'll attend to them later on, personally,

01:27:48.010 --> 01:27:49.040
they can be attended to;

